title: Canoe & Kayak - May 2016
description:
English | 76 pages | PDF | 33.9 MB

Backed by 40 years of experience, Canoe & Kayak magazine is the world's leading paddlesports publication. We keep it simple: Live, breathe, paddle. In oceans and lakes, in the surf and down the river. We provide the techniques, destinations, videos, photos and stories that inspire you to get on the water. Our collective readership constitutes the largest group of paddlers anywhere on the planet
